ggplot(dat, aes(x = normal, y = ratio, color = IF)) +
  geom_point(size = .1) +
  scale_x_log10() +
  scale_y_log10() +
  scale_color_discrete()

dat %>% group_by(IF) %>% 
  summarise(medianRatio = median(ratio))
rage <- read_tsv("tmp/RAGE_binding.txt", col_names = "name")

  scale_x_log10() +
  scale_y_log10() +
  scale_color_discrete()


dat %>% filter(!is.na(ratio)) %>% 
  group_by(RAGE) %>% 
  summarise(medianRatio = median(ratio))
